      "file_path": "blueprints-processor/adaptors/data-adaptor-provider/pom.xml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 28,
      "message": "binding-parent 1.5.1-SNAPSHOT currently has ccsdk.sli.core.version defined as 0.7.0-SNAPSHOT\nand abpove property is forcing sli-core to be on same version as ccsdk/features module which is wrong.\n\nWe should be able to release ccsdk/features without releasing sli-core.\n\nIf we override above property with project.version then during release of ccsdk/features version will become 1.5.1 and there will not be any sli-core with same version.",
